items.title: SpiceJet Q3 results: Airline swings to black with Rs 25 crore net profit
items.description: The revenue for both Q2FY25 and Q3FY25 came in at Rs 852.8 crore and Rs 1,140.66 crore, respectively, lower from Rs 1,425.29 crore seen in Q2FY24 and Rs 1,756.6 crore in Q3FY24

items.title: Tesla market value slips below $1 trillion as Europe sales sink
items.description: Tesla shares are now by far the biggest decliner among the mega-cap technology stocks, weighing heavily on the group’s overall performance
